{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review modern slavery laws to prevent use of child labour in chocolate industry",
        "additional_details": "We want the Government to ensure that companies which produce chocolate in the UK most be able to prove that child labour has not been used in the production process. If companies are found to use child labour, the Government should prevent them from trading in the UK. This will protect the consumer, as they can be certain that they are not unwillingly supporting a company that uses child labour.",
